OL,3,COne in four unpaid carers in Wales
OL,4,Clive in poverty, report finds
OL,6,FA new report claims that 26% of unpaid
OL,7,Fcarers in Wales live in poverty, with
OL,8,F9% experiencing deep poverty - figures
OL,9,Fsignificantly higher than the non-
OL,10,Fcarer population.
OL,12,FThe report by WPI Economics and Carers
OL,13,FWales also found many unpaid carers
OL,14,Fare forced to reduce their working
OL,15,Fhours or leave employment entirely due
OL,16,Fto their caring responsibilities,
OL,17,Fexacerbating their financial
OL,18,Fdifficulties.
