OL,3,COne in four unpaid carers in Wales
OL,4,Clive in poverty, report finds
OL,6,FRob Simkins, Head of Policy and Public
OL,7,FAffairs of Carers Wales said: "The
OL,8,Ffindings ofJthis report clearly show
OL,9,Fthe need for urgent action.
OL,11,F"Unpaid carers in Wales provide
OL,12,Finvaluable care, often at great cost
OL,13,Fto their own health and wellbeing, as
OL,14,Fwell as their own finances.
OL,16,F"Research shows that in Wales alone,
OL,17,Fthe care provided by Wales'unpaid
OL,18,Fcarers saves the state over #10
OL,19,Fbillion per year and has a huge impact
OL,20,Fon the wellbeing of the people they
OL,21,Fprovide care for.
